channel.title: ~ What is the name of this Server ~
channel.description:
Hey guys, I had a question, i've seen this server somewhere on moparscape and i've searched through server downloads yet I still can't seem to find it. It has... -Max Capes -Minecraft Remodeled people as shop -Also has Falcon & Creepers as Shop people -Has cool gear like voodoo masks, griffon mask, armadyl armor, and tons of other gear in donator shop -I believe the home is in the Rogue's Den -Pretty sure revision is 600 or less.
If you know this server, could you please post a link to where I could find it ~ Thanks!
